College Station, United States - May 06, 2025 On May 6, X user Chris G shared a video showing flooded streets in College Station, located in Brazos County. The video was recorded from a moving car and shows vehicles driving through heavy floodwaters caused by a storm. Chris G simply captioned the post: College Station flooding.
